{
  "id": "RAW_603cd806",
  "title": "惯犯 Cursor 又来\"自研\"了，还是熟悉的配方，国产模型套壳",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247501621&idx=1&sn=b83831c7b488d23bfe5751bf0eeaae19",
  "date": "2026-03-21 05:27:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>刘小排</span> <span>2026-03-21 13:27</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=afc4f962&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fq6aOmBZKAbNkgIfzByeiab8XWtNfFr5UTqdMZAmWmA5SXmxiacdXcic9zMdURbVTJmtH3AZLcbQ3eiaRhvvjPxG4lnrRNvSiaVxlMZUgLMSnJqfE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>以前美国一开源，中国就\"自研\"。现在中国一开源，美国就\"自研\"。</p>\n  <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin: 0 auto;padding: 24px 20px 48px 20px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前上学的时候，有句话叫\"美国一开源，中国就自研\"——讽刺的是中国公司拿开源模型换个皮就说自主可控。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在风水轮流转了。</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">中国一开源，美国就\"自研\"。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天这事我又能笑一天——硅谷最火的AI编程工具Cursor，刚刚又双叒叕被抓了个大包。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么回事呢？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3月19日，Cursor高调发布了自家\"自研\"模型Composer 2。发布会上的说法是：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们做了持续预训练，又做了大规模强化学习，性价比吊打Claude Opus 4.6和GPT-5.4。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">好家伙，一夜之间，硅谷科技媒体集体高潮：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor要跟OpenAI和Anthropic正面硬刚了！</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100017967\" data-ratio=\"0.9083333333333333\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 8px;display:block;width:100%;max-width:100%;height:auto;margin:30px auto !important;padding:8px !important;border-radius:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.22), 0 4px 10px rgba(15,23,42,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6874c198&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbM3vPYkzvHMqFX74eJQmxxSDssUZZwj3q2PUmrIx4zqDH2QsghCnVBfdD6U73VkDAic33S2pJRUVE8pcF1y8AAfh5EvFCtia6qdE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">仅仅过了不到3个小时，就翻车了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个开发者在调试Cursor的API请求时，发现了一个不得了的东西——Composer 2的真实模型ID是：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, monospace;padding: 3px 6px;background-color: #fff5f5 !important;color: #d71a1b !important;border-radius: 4px;font-size: 13px !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">kimi-k2p5-rl-0317-s515-fast</span></code></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你不需要懂技术也能读懂这串字符。kimi-k2p5，就是月之暗面的Kimi K2.5。rl，就是强化学习。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100017968\" data-ratio=\"1.1018518518518519\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 8px;display:block;width:100%;max-width:100%;height:auto;margin:30px auto !important;padding:8px !important;border-radius:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.22), 0 4px 10px rgba(15,23,42,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c2ff529b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbPfwHvXERjQTJQTGRHBJuBD3DicuEybcEyQWLoN9WrHDmNrAn6rt2XWoSNnKPvvf6Fb2wpkV7z5licmGA3VcbeKMoIcGTuSjKkNY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">翻译成人话就是：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所谓\"自研\"的Composer 2，就是拿了中国公司月之暗面的开源模型Kimi K2.5，做了一轮强化学习微调，然后换了个名字端上来的。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi预训练负责人杜育伦直接在推特上@了Cursor联合创始人Michael Truell，说：我们测试了Composer 2的tokenizer，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">和Kimi的tokenizer完全一致。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">几乎可以确定，这就是我们的模型被进一步微调的结果。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后杜总问了一个很直白的问题：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么不遵守我们的许可证？为什么没有付费？ （注：杜总现在已经删除了这条）</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个问题问得好啊。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5的开源许可证里写得清清楚楚：如果你的商业产品月收入超过2000万美元，必须在用户界面上</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">显著展示\"Kimi K2.5\"字样。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor的母公司Anysphere，估值290亿美金，年收入超过20亿美元——月收入大概1.67亿美元，是门槛的</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">8倍以上。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但Cursor的界面上，只写了\"Composer 2\"。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个字都没提Kimi。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可爱的马老师也发来了嘲讽</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21203703703703702\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 8px;display:block;width:100%;max-width:100%;height:auto;margin:30px auto !important;padding:8px !important;border-radius:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.22), 0 4px 10px rgba(15,23,42,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100017965\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=864b04cb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbNd3LxwUwB1QM6W6eZLhEaWY1FG53BmyQn9WzxBE5oibdtcicWb2o0AAk6mrcfZsUHWzOrzp1lZq2yibhh3bicVzicFGY62G3D5I1XY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为对比，Kimi官方Twitter显得非常大度和体面</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5518518518518518\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 8px;display:block;width:100%;max-width:100%;height:auto;margin:30px auto !important;padding:8px !important;border-radius:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.22), 0 4px 10px rgba(15,23,42,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100017966\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e2ca97e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbOK8UjoAgGzX3JuezCqCww7dYv8pcGibiaRc7IZ30WIBibjicnjBcU22CkA1ib5Nm7saelNiaJXYGw7HpsicEHKdciaUzJSpouUlLammAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你以为这是第一次？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor上一代模型Composer 1，也被扒出来大概率是基于阿里的通义千问Qwen。证据是用户发现Cursor生成的代码里，时不时冒出中文字符。当时有人在社区问Cursor的研究员：你们的模型到底是不是基于开源模型微调的？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor研究员的回答非常经典——他没说是，也没说不是，只说了一句：\"我们的重点在RL后训练上。\"</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈哈哈哈，好一个\"重点在RL后训练\"。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">就好比你问一个厨师：\"这道菜是不是用的预制菜？\"他回答你：\"我们的重点在摆盘上。\"</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且不止Cursor一家。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Windsurf——就是那个被Google DeepMind数十亿美金收购的编程工具——它的SWE-1.5模型也被发现底层其实是智谱AI的GLM模型。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为曾经全世界科技创新灯塔的硅谷，现在已经纷纷痴迷于预制菜摆盘技术了吗？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其实我个人对\"用开源模型做产品\"这件事本身一点意见都没有——开源的意义就在于此，全世界都可以用，这是好事。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但你不能一边用着别人的模型，一边假装这是自己的，还违反开源协议、花那么多心思把人家名字全部去掉、藏起来。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这叫什么？这叫又当又立。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">中国AI团队在开源社区贡献了Kimi K2.5、Qwen、DeepSeek、GLM这些优秀的模型，硅谷公司拿去用了，用了就用了，大大方方承认多好？在界面上写一行\"Powered by Kimi K2.5\"，既合规又体面，还能显得你有眼光。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果呢你偷偷用了，还要包装成自研，被抓包了还不回应。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor的评论区全是一种声音：“你敢不敢说Kimi两个字？”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d71a1b !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过两天的半推半就，Cursor现在终于算是勉强回应了，语气中中一万个不情愿</span></strong></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;margin: 16px 0;border: none !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr style=\"border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n      <td style=\"padding: 0 4px;vertical-align: top;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.837037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0;border-radius: 8px;height: auto;display:block;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017969\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a81f7b94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbMMnZZchTpIyWKfwVbT60Knyib2m6gJvtDqLMWKhmia4nHksL9SmpEVLToZKAfoxFsUxLwicboyKE0Sia0l32ONZPU6iaSaqyfqrhtA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 0 4px;vertical-align: top;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100017970\" data-ratio=\"0.6185185185185185\" style=\"margin: 0;border-radius: 8px;height: auto;display:block;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f647db6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbNGVHib61bM2dxbTwSaJVicsPC05XaIAicHLz6e18NZ6AMqP9lGicB82zJH77N328FYznDQRWteeM87ZJSPByoVOHDQGCR5SQPanfo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">290亿美金的估值，连一句\"谢谢\"都难说出口。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这事儿啊，不丢Kimi的人，丢的是Cursor的人。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\">以前美国一开源，中国就\"自研\"。现在中国一开源，美国就\"自研\"。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">时代真的变了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #333333 !important;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">期待你的想法，评论区见！</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=1d90614f&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI1MTUxNzgxMA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247501621%26idx%3D1%26sn%3Db83831c7b488d23bfe5751bf0eeaae19\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文披露了 AI 编程工具 Cursor 声称自研的 Composer 2 模型实际上是基于中国公司月之暗面的 Kimi K2.5 开源模型微调而来，且未遵守开源协议标注来源，批评其“又当又立”的行为。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文披露了 AI 编程工具 Cursor 声称自研的 Composer 2 模型实际上是基于中国公司月之暗面的 Kimi K2.5 开源模型微调而来，且未遵守开源协议标注来源，批评其“又当又立”的行为。",
  "summary": "文章详细报道了硅谷 AI 编程工具 Cursor 的又一次\"自研\"闹剧。2026 年 3 月 19 日，Cursor 高调发布 Composer 2，声称通过持续预训练和大规模强化学习自研而成，性价比吊打 Claude 和 GPT。然而仅过 3 小时，有开发者发现其真实模型 ID 为 kimi-k2p5-rl-0317-s515-fast，意味着 Composer 2 实际是基于月之暗面的 Kimi K2.5 开源模型微调而来。Kimi 团队确认 tokenizer 完全一致，并质疑 Cursor 为何不遵守开源协议（要求月收入超 2000 万美元时显著标注 Kimi）。文章还提及 Cursor 上一代 Composer 1 也被扒出基于阿里通义千问，Windsurf 也被发现底层使用智谱 AI 的 GLM 模型。作者批评这种使用开源模型却伪装自研、违反开源协议的行为是“又当又立”，感慨风水轮流转。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Cursor Composer 2 被证实是基于 Kimi K2.5 开源模型微调而来，真实模型 ID 暴露了底层模型来源。",
      "explanation": "开发者发现 Composer 2 的 API 请求中模型 ID 包含 kimi-k2p5-rl-0317-s515-fast，Kimi 团队确认 tokenizer 完全一致，基本证实了套壳行为。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Cursor 涉嫌违反 Kimi K2.5 开源许可证，未按要求在月收入超 2000 万美元时标注 Kimi 来源。",
      "explanation": "Cursor 母公司 Anysphere 估值 290 亿美元，年收入超 20 亿美元，月收入约 1.67 亿美元，是许可门槛的 8 倍以上，但界面未标注任何 Kimi 相关信息。"
    },
    {
      "point": "这并非 Cursor 首次被发现使用开源模型——Composer 1 也曾被扒出基于阿里通义千问。",
      "explanation": "用户发现 Cursor 生成的代码中偶尔出现中文字符，引发社区质疑，Cursor 研究员仅回应\"重点在 RL 后训练\"，未正面否认。"
    },
    {
      "point": "使用开源模型本身无可厚非，但伪装自研、违反开源协议、刻意隐藏来源是行业不诚信行为。",
      "explanation": "开源模型供全世界使用是好事，但应大大方方承认并按许可证要求标注来源，而非包装成自研并移除所有痕迹。"
    },
    {
      "point": "中国 AI 开源模型正在获得全球认可，从\"中国自研\"到\"美国自研\"反映了中国技术实力的提升。",
      "explanation": "从讽刺中国公司拿开源模型换皮，到硅谷公司纷纷基于中国开源模型做产品，风水轮流转体现了中国 AI 技术的进步。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "所谓\"自研\"的 Composer 2，就是拿了中国公司月之暗面的开源模型 Kimi K2.5，做了一轮强化学习微调，然后换了个名字端上来的。",
    "这叫什么？这叫又当又立。",
